1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:08,000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

2
00:01:02,540 --> 00:01:04,100
[The Eternal Fragrance]

3
00:01:04,100 --> 00:01:07,980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

4
00:01:08,020 --> 00:01:11,140
[Episode 6]

5
00:01:29,520 --> 00:01:30,220
Leave now.

6
00:01:37,910 --> 00:01:39,010
What are you doing? Are you crazy?

7
00:02:08,240 --> 00:02:10,220
Your Highness, what brings you here?

8
00:02:15,150 --> 00:02:15,940
No time to explain.

9
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:16,810
Run!

10
00:03:35,550 --> 00:03:36,220
Run!

11
00:04:04,240 --> 00:04:05,020
- There's an exit! - Go.

12
00:04:10,870 --> 00:04:11,410
Mr. Zuo,

13
00:04:11,760 --> 00:04:13,410
no sign of intruders in Wuxing Pavilion.

14
00:04:13,670 --> 00:04:14,650
All warding seals are intact,

15
00:04:14,830 --> 00:04:16,130
no odd spirit aura detected.

16
00:04:17,150 --> 00:04:18,180
That green light

17
00:04:18,760 --> 00:04:20,180
is the Divine Tree's aura.

18
00:04:20,590 --> 00:04:22,540
I definitely got it right.

19
00:04:25,270 --> 00:04:25,810
Mr. Zuo!

20
00:04:27,320 --> 00:04:27,890
Mr. Zuo!

21
00:04:29,270 --> 00:04:30,300
What's going on?

22
00:04:30,520 --> 00:04:31,420
Who broke in?

23
00:04:31,640 --> 00:04:32,180
Jiaping,

24
00:04:32,760 --> 00:04:35,210
are you carrying the key to the Futu Tower?

25
00:04:35,320 --> 00:04:35,740
Yes,

26
00:04:38,560 --> 00:04:39,740
I've kept it with me at all times.

27
00:04:43,270 --> 00:04:44,660
The tower is wrapped in heavy restriction spells.

28
00:04:45,270 --> 00:04:46,370
Anyone breaking in without the key

29
00:04:46,830 --> 00:04:47,980
will trigger alarms.

30
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:05,100
I slept dead to the world last night

31
00:05:05,200 --> 00:05:06,660
and didn't feel anything off.

32
00:05:12,590 --> 00:05:13,980
None of the restriction spells around

33
00:05:14,470 --> 00:05:15,890
are cracked or loose.

34
00:05:16,760 --> 00:05:18,660
Was the intruder strong enough

35
00:05:19,230 --> 00:05:20,620
to come through solid rock?

36
00:05:23,120 --> 00:05:23,690
Or

37
00:05:24,080 --> 00:05:25,810
hidden paths we don't know about?

38
00:05:28,230 --> 00:05:28,940
I'll search again.

39
00:05:34,960 --> 00:05:35,420
Mr. Zuo,

40
00:05:36,080 --> 00:05:37,940
my master, Elder Xuanshan, said

41
00:05:38,350 --> 00:05:39,570
the Divine Tree disappeared

42
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:41,660
after the Sea Calamity ages ago.

43
00:05:44,270 --> 00:05:45,420
It hasn't been seen

44
00:05:46,880 --> 00:05:48,690
in the past five centuries.

45
00:05:50,760 --> 00:05:51,370
Seems bad things

46
00:05:52,710 --> 00:05:54,940
are coming to this academy.

47
00:06:03,830 --> 00:06:04,810
Don't you remember

48
00:06:05,200 --> 00:06:06,450
what happened back then?

49
00:06:09,320 --> 00:06:10,890
I was training with The Record of Spirit Release.

50
00:06:12,320 --> 00:06:13,860
I pulled in some spirit energy,

51
00:06:14,910 --> 00:06:16,330
but messed up the technique.

52
00:06:18,080 --> 00:06:19,130
I can't remember clearly.

53
00:06:19,470 --> 00:06:20,060
Xiuyuan,

54
00:06:20,320 --> 00:06:21,250
did you see anything?

55
00:06:23,910 --> 00:06:25,810
Your aura was unstable,

56
00:06:26,270 --> 00:06:26,980
and you lacked spirit power,

57
00:06:27,520 --> 00:06:28,940
so I tried to stabilize your spirit aura.

58
00:06:30,440 --> 00:06:32,770
Then a blast of power knocked me flying.

59
00:06:37,520 --> 00:06:39,860
Any pain anywhere?

60
00:06:41,710 --> 00:06:42,250
Or

61
00:06:42,910 --> 00:06:43,940
feel any different at all?

62
00:06:47,270 --> 00:06:47,890
Nothing.

63
00:06:49,910 --> 00:06:51,250
I don't feel any different at all.

64
00:06:52,790 --> 00:06:54,210
Could we have triggered

65
00:06:55,350 --> 00:06:56,330
some ancient restriction spells?

66
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:59,370
There are countless ancient books.

67
00:06:59,590 --> 00:07:00,690
Runes cover shelves

68
00:07:00,710 --> 00:07:01,540
and floors alike.

69
00:07:01,560 --> 00:07:02,500
We never know what we touched.

70
00:07:04,270 --> 00:07:05,450
Leave other matters aside.

71
00:07:05,790 --> 00:07:07,210
The trouble at the Script Tower has blown up.

72
00:07:07,520 --> 00:07:08,980
What if our teachers question us?

73
00:07:10,120 --> 00:07:11,420
If the Disciplinary Pavilion finds out,

74
00:07:11,640 --> 00:07:12,770
we'll face harsh punishment.

75
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:14,330
We might

76
00:07:14,640 --> 00:07:15,740
get expelled from the academy.

77
00:07:22,350 --> 00:07:23,130
Have you heard?

78
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:25,130
Someone broke into the Futu Tower last night.

79
00:07:25,480 --> 00:07:26,170
The Futu Tower?

80
00:07:26,270 --> 00:07:27,250
Can't believe that it happened.

81
00:07:27,270 --> 00:07:27,770
Indeed.

82
00:07:38,270 --> 00:07:39,500
Xiuyuan, Lifei,

83
00:07:40,560 --> 00:07:41,060
come here.

84
00:07:41,710 --> 00:07:42,130
Come here.

85
00:07:44,270 --> 00:07:45,450
This is Yue Cailing,

86
00:07:45,470 --> 00:07:46,980
favored disciple of Immortal Guangwei

87
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:48,500
from the Wuyue Court.

88
00:07:50,640 --> 00:07:52,940
This is Qin Yangling,

89
00:07:53,150 --> 00:07:54,620
chief disciple of Elder Cuixuan.

90
00:07:58,520 --> 00:08:00,330
My master, Immortal Guangwei, has heard

91
00:08:00,350 --> 00:08:01,540
of Lei's extraordinary talent.

92
00:08:01,910 --> 00:08:03,740
He sent me here with an offer.

93
00:08:07,350 --> 00:08:09,370
Once you finish your studies,

94
00:08:09,760 --> 00:08:11,250
would you like to cultivate at the Wuyue Court?

95
00:08:14,880 --> 00:08:15,860
Thanks for the kind offer.

96
00:08:16,150 --> 00:08:18,210
But I've only been here for less than a month,

97
00:08:18,590 --> 00:08:19,660
so I need more time to cultivate.

98
00:08:21,710 --> 00:08:23,180
I've got things to do. I'm leaving.

99
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:24,370
Wait.

100
00:08:26,030 --> 00:08:26,940
No, he…

101
00:08:28,030 --> 00:08:30,010
He's just quiet and bad with words.

102
00:08:30,230 --> 00:08:31,620
Deep down, he'd love to go.

103
00:08:31,640 --> 00:08:32,490
Absolutely.

104
00:08:34,870 --> 00:08:37,180
The immortal sects shall select a year later.

105
00:08:37,510 --> 00:08:38,970
Why recruit this early?

106
00:08:44,440 --> 00:08:46,260
The academy's Futu Tower was broken in.

107
00:08:46,750 --> 00:08:48,730
It houses ancient books from all immortal sects across the nine states.

108
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:49,970
This is extremely critical,

109
00:08:50,440 --> 00:08:51,780
so we merely came to help.

110
00:08:56,160 --> 00:08:56,690
Xiuyuan.

111
00:08:57,630 --> 00:08:58,780
Zong Quan is here again.

112
00:09:52,680 --> 00:09:55,940
Last night, someone snuck into the forbidden Futu Tower.

113
00:09:57,280 --> 00:09:58,690
If any of you did,

114
00:09:59,960 --> 00:10:01,180
step forward voluntarily.

115
00:10:05,350 --> 00:10:06,490
I'd never dare to do such a thing!

116
00:10:06,510 --> 00:10:07,730
No thief would stick around afterward.

117
00:10:07,750 --> 00:10:08,450
Who was it?

118
00:10:09,470 --> 00:10:10,690
- Don't drag everyone down! - Yes.

119
00:10:16,960 --> 00:10:17,490
What?

120
00:10:18,440 --> 00:10:19,780
None of you dares admit?

121
00:10:24,440 --> 00:10:24,940
Jiaping.

122
00:10:37,960 --> 00:10:38,540
You'll handle this.

123
00:10:48,710 --> 00:10:50,970
Since none of you admit it,

124
00:10:51,680 --> 00:10:55,020
I'll have the script spirits in the tower to identify the intruder.

125
00:12:10,990 --> 00:12:12,260
The script spirits found

126
00:12:12,440 --> 00:12:14,780
no trace of the tower aura on any disciple.

127
00:12:18,160 --> 00:12:19,210
In this case,

128
00:12:20,320 --> 00:12:22,260
the intruder can't be one of our academy.

129
00:12:27,200 --> 00:12:30,690
Alright, you may all disperse.

130
00:12:31,800 --> 00:12:32,540
Wait a moment.

131
00:12:39,200 --> 00:12:42,540
Strange spirit aura lingered above the Futu Tower,

132
00:12:42,920 --> 00:12:44,970
most likely related to the Sea Calamity.

133
00:12:45,830 --> 00:12:47,690
It concerns the safety of the nine states.

134
00:12:48,280 --> 00:12:49,730
How can you brush it off so lightly?

135
00:12:51,510 --> 00:12:54,140
What do you want to do, Mr. Zong?

136
00:12:56,830 --> 00:13:00,450
The Longming Sanctuary's treasure, Spirit-searching Branch,

137
00:13:01,110 --> 00:13:03,810
is capable of tracking rare spirit auras.

138
00:13:04,510 --> 00:13:06,850
I'd like to give it a try.

139
00:13:42,590 --> 00:13:44,020
Oh, no! I'm exposed.

140
00:14:09,990 --> 00:14:10,900
You again!

141
00:14:14,400 --> 00:14:15,730
Meet your end!

142
00:14:20,160 --> 00:14:20,690
Xiuyuan!

143
00:14:30,960 --> 00:14:31,660
Xiuyuan!

144
00:14:36,320 --> 00:14:37,180
You're seeking death!

145
00:15:26,680 --> 00:15:27,380
Xiuyuan!

146
00:15:34,080 --> 00:15:35,020
Mr. Zong!

147
00:15:40,750 --> 00:15:41,900
- Xiuyuan! - Xiuyuan!

148
00:15:42,320 --> 00:15:43,210
Lifei, are you alright?

149
00:15:54,680 --> 00:15:55,490
What was I thinking?

150
00:15:56,800 --> 00:15:57,940
Had Mr. Zuo not intervened,

151
00:15:58,680 --> 00:16:00,330
I would've sacrificed myself to save Lifei.

152
00:16:03,470 --> 00:16:05,970
Mr. Zuo is said to be the top hidden cultivator across the nine states.

153
00:16:06,560 --> 00:16:07,730
Your power is truly unfathomable.

154
00:16:11,160 --> 00:16:11,780
Zuo Qiu,

155
00:16:12,870 --> 00:16:13,690
you were

156
00:16:13,990 --> 00:16:16,900
close friends with that traitor cultivator years ago.

157
00:16:17,470 --> 00:16:18,610
Since this spirit aura has resurfaced,

158
00:16:18,870 --> 00:16:20,450
your academy cannot escape blame.

159
00:16:20,990 --> 00:16:24,060
That man once led us to fight the Sea Calamity.

160
00:16:24,440 --> 00:16:26,330
The Longming Sanctuary took the hardest hit,

161
00:16:26,680 --> 00:16:28,090
so you shared a deep connection.

162
00:16:29,110 --> 00:16:31,260
Mr. Zong, do not make excuses

163
00:16:31,590 --> 00:16:32,570
to hurt my students.

164
00:16:34,800 --> 00:16:35,730
Are they students?

165
00:16:36,280 --> 00:16:37,610
They are murderers, obviously.

166
00:16:38,230 --> 00:16:38,570
You!

167
00:16:38,590 --> 00:16:41,380
He alone slew several of my disciples.

168
00:16:41,750 --> 00:16:43,420
All of them are his accomplices.

169
00:16:45,160 --> 00:16:47,900
I shall take them back

170
00:16:48,160 --> 00:16:50,020
to offer sacrifice for my fallen disciples.

171
00:16:50,750 --> 00:16:51,380
Bah!

172
00:16:52,400 --> 00:16:54,300
The Longming Sanctuary aided the wicked.

173
00:16:54,320 --> 00:16:55,300
Cruel and heartless,

174
00:16:55,470 --> 00:16:57,180
you ravaged Gaolu and slaughtered its people.

175
00:16:57,560 --> 00:16:59,850
Yeah, besides Xiuyuan,

176
00:17:00,230 --> 00:17:02,850
Gelin, Changyue and I

177
00:17:03,230 --> 00:17:04,940
are all survivors of Gaolu.

178
00:17:05,270 --> 00:17:06,140
We've scraped by

179
00:17:06,640 --> 00:17:08,620
all these years just to stay alive,

180
00:17:09,160 --> 00:17:09,940
yet you

181
00:17:10,550 --> 00:17:12,100
still hunt us without end.

182
00:17:12,510 --> 00:17:15,210
Countless cultivators walk this world.

183
00:17:16,230 --> 00:17:18,490
Shall your baseless words

184
00:17:18,680 --> 00:17:21,180
brand the Longming Sanctuary as killers?

185
00:17:24,440 --> 00:17:25,970
That day at the Yange Hall in Lugong Town,

186
00:17:26,270 --> 00:17:27,530
your disciples burst in suddenly

187
00:17:27,550 --> 00:17:28,730
and tried to take my life.

188
00:17:29,160 --> 00:17:30,660
As a senior of the immortal sects,

189
00:17:31,160 --> 00:17:33,140
you ordered your disciples to wield immortal arts recklessly

190
00:17:33,160 --> 00:17:33,940
and slay the innocent.

191
00:17:34,920 --> 00:17:36,050
Xiuyuan and the others only defended themselves.

192
00:17:36,750 --> 00:17:37,490
What's wrong with that?

193
00:17:43,440 --> 00:17:47,730
As the immortal sect protecting Wugou,

194
00:17:47,880 --> 00:17:50,050
we only followed orders to wipe out rebels.

195
00:17:50,400 --> 00:17:52,250
Rebels all deserve to die.

196
00:17:52,270 --> 00:17:54,450
Are you out of your mind?

197
00:17:55,070 --> 00:17:56,380
They were just kids seven years ago.

198
00:17:56,400 --> 00:17:57,490
How were they rebels?

199
00:17:58,160 --> 00:17:58,820
Moreover,

200
00:17:59,230 --> 00:18:01,010
they lived fine on their own land,

201
00:18:01,030 --> 00:18:01,940
but you took their territory

202
00:18:01,960 --> 00:18:02,860
and called them rebels.

203
00:18:02,920 --> 00:18:04,180
Using your logic, cops should arrest

204
00:18:04,200 --> 00:18:05,490
homeowners instead of thieves!

205
00:18:07,710 --> 00:18:08,420
Plus,

206
00:18:09,120 --> 00:18:11,450
your top disciples,

207
00:18:12,070 --> 00:18:13,210
picked on regular people,

208
00:18:13,230 --> 00:18:14,250
only to get killed by them.

209
00:18:14,710 --> 00:18:15,730
If I were you,

210
00:18:15,960 --> 00:18:17,250
I'd have hidden this embarrassment forever.

211
00:18:17,440 --> 00:18:18,380
How shameless!

212
00:18:21,470 --> 00:18:23,100
Still arguing nonsense.

213
00:18:23,600 --> 00:18:25,290
The Spirit-searching Branch

214
00:18:25,510 --> 00:18:27,050
pointed right at you before it broke.

215
00:18:27,400 --> 00:18:29,490
The strange aura over the Futu Tower

216
00:18:29,710 --> 00:18:30,580
must have something to do with you.

217
00:18:31,200 --> 00:18:31,530
I...

218
00:18:33,070 --> 00:18:35,140
Zuo Qiu, can't you see

219
00:18:35,230 --> 00:18:36,100
what's really happening?

220
00:18:42,960 --> 00:18:43,690
Mr. Zong,

221
00:18:45,440 --> 00:18:47,290
they've not been in the academy long

222
00:18:47,680 --> 00:18:48,580
and aren't strong enough

223
00:18:49,120 --> 00:18:51,180
to get past the restriction spells in the Futu Tower.

224
00:18:51,600 --> 00:18:53,620
We need to look into this properly.

225
00:18:53,880 --> 00:18:55,730
Don't convict them right away.

226
00:18:58,750 --> 00:18:59,450
Very well.

227
00:18:59,790 --> 00:19:01,940
I shall stay here

228
00:19:02,200 --> 00:19:03,450
and await your word.

229
00:19:11,230 --> 00:19:11,820
Alright.

230
00:19:12,680 --> 00:19:14,490
This matter ends for today.

231
00:19:15,440 --> 00:19:16,530
Everyone, disperse.

232
00:19:28,960 --> 00:19:29,530
Elder Zhu,

233
00:19:31,920 --> 00:19:34,050
take Lei Xiuyuan to heal his wounds.

234
00:19:35,600 --> 00:19:36,010
Understood.

235
00:19:56,550 --> 00:19:59,690
Zong Quan's Golden Light Formation stabs deep to the core,

236
00:20:00,160 --> 00:20:02,010
yet it should not hurt you this severely.

237
00:20:05,920 --> 00:20:07,690
Why didn't you resist with your spirit power?

238
00:20:14,200 --> 00:20:15,140
Xiuyuan

239
00:20:16,440 --> 00:20:17,820
gave me all his spirit power.

240
00:20:20,880 --> 00:20:22,900
No wonder you were untouched

241
00:20:23,640 --> 00:20:25,250
amid the golden light.

242
00:20:28,120 --> 00:20:29,900
He risked his own life for you.

243
00:20:30,680 --> 00:20:31,820
Such a youthful bond

244
00:20:31,840 --> 00:20:32,940
is truly precious.

245
00:20:33,680 --> 00:20:35,340
I shall prepare the medicine.

246
00:20:42,710 --> 00:20:43,730
What were you thinking

247
00:20:44,200 --> 00:20:45,050
when you saved me?

248
00:20:48,790 --> 00:20:49,770
Nothing at all.

249
00:20:52,550 --> 00:20:53,340
Were you not afraid of dying?

250
00:20:54,600 --> 00:20:55,140
I was.

251
00:20:58,880 --> 00:21:02,340
But Zong Quan never intended to spare me.

252
00:21:04,680 --> 00:21:08,820
Better one perishes than both.

253
00:21:11,550 --> 00:21:12,420
I passed my power to you,

254
00:21:13,680 --> 00:21:14,820
and you could seek out your master.

255
00:21:15,710 --> 00:21:16,580
Life is harsh;

256
00:21:19,120 --> 00:21:20,340
at least you could fulfill your wish.

257
00:21:32,360 --> 00:21:34,290
Lifei, where are you going?

258
00:21:35,160 --> 00:21:36,340
To demand justice from our teachers.

259
00:21:43,200 --> 00:21:44,340
Xiuyuan, how do you feel?

260
00:21:49,200 --> 00:21:49,770
Mr. Zhu,

261
00:21:50,880 --> 00:21:52,050
how is Xiuyuan's injury?

262
00:21:52,400 --> 00:21:53,210
What can we do to help?

263
00:21:53,750 --> 00:21:54,860
His meridians are damaged.

264
00:21:55,470 --> 00:21:57,250
Someone must channel spirit power into him nonstop.

265
00:21:57,710 --> 00:21:58,250
I volunteer!

266
00:21:59,230 --> 00:22:00,210
We all do.

267
00:22:02,120 --> 00:22:02,730
Xiuyuan,

268
00:22:03,470 --> 00:22:04,940
you've endured countless hardships,

269
00:22:05,120 --> 00:22:06,530
yet your friends

270
00:22:06,790 --> 00:22:07,940
treat you with all their hearts.

271
00:22:08,550 --> 00:22:10,340
Hard times will surely give way to good fortune.

272
00:22:14,230 --> 00:22:14,860
Thank you.

273
00:22:15,710 --> 00:22:18,100
We owe you thanks.

274
00:22:18,640 --> 00:22:19,420
We only wish

275
00:22:19,750 --> 00:22:20,970
you'd stop worrying over us from now on.

276
00:22:21,960 --> 00:22:23,860
Whether it's the Longming Sanctuary or Zong Quan,

277
00:22:24,550 --> 00:22:25,450
we'll stand together.

278
00:22:27,470 --> 00:22:28,140
Alright.

279
00:22:29,550 --> 00:22:31,290
Though Zong Quan rules an immortal sect,

280
00:22:32,120 --> 00:22:34,770
he's petty and cruel.

281
00:22:35,120 --> 00:22:36,380
You slew his disciples

282
00:22:36,550 --> 00:22:37,940
and he'll never let you off easily.

283
00:22:38,200 --> 00:22:39,660
Steer clear of him,

284
00:22:40,310 --> 00:22:41,450
and never face him alone.

285
00:22:42,600 --> 00:22:44,250
That strange aura is the Divine Tree.

286
00:22:44,990 --> 00:22:45,690
Yes.

287
00:22:47,070 --> 00:22:49,580
The Divine Tree absorbing heaven and earth's spirit energy

288
00:22:50,200 --> 00:22:51,900
has been lost for hundreds of years, right?

289
00:22:52,400 --> 00:22:54,180
Zong Quan came to the academy

290
00:22:54,470 --> 00:22:55,820
just to hunt for the Divine Tree.

291
00:22:56,470 --> 00:22:57,450
Do not engage him

292
00:22:58,030 --> 00:22:58,810
[Xuanshanzi, Xingzheng Hall]

293
00:22:58,810 --> 00:23:00,140
in direct conflict unless necessary.

294
00:23:05,920 --> 00:23:07,530
Are you alright?

295
00:23:08,440 --> 00:23:10,770
I'm fine, just an old wound.

296
00:23:11,230 --> 00:23:14,100
The Sea Calamity draws near; time waits for none.

297
00:23:14,750 --> 00:23:16,820
The Divine Tree holds Yue's fate.

298
00:23:17,200 --> 00:23:19,180
Find out where it is at once.

299
00:23:24,600 --> 00:23:25,290
Mr. Zuo,

300
00:23:25,750 --> 00:23:26,770
Zong Quan is hunting

301
00:23:26,790 --> 00:23:28,450
Xiuyuan and me.

302
00:23:28,920 --> 00:23:30,420
You have to protect us.

303
00:23:39,750 --> 00:23:40,250
Sit.

304
00:23:44,230 --> 00:23:46,770
Did many spirits

305
00:23:47,360 --> 00:23:49,490
draw near you in Qingqiu?

306
00:23:52,600 --> 00:23:53,900
Besides,

307
00:23:55,120 --> 00:23:58,690
when I traveled with my master,

308
00:23:59,310 --> 00:24:01,340
all kinds of spirits

309
00:24:01,710 --> 00:24:03,290
often lingered around me.

310
00:24:03,680 --> 00:24:04,900
My master warned me repeatedly

311
00:24:05,120 --> 00:24:06,660
never to tell others.

312
00:24:09,750 --> 00:24:10,420
Mr. Zuo,

313
00:24:11,990 --> 00:24:13,250
will something bad happen to me?

314
00:24:17,230 --> 00:24:19,450
After a tiring day, you must be hungry.

315
00:24:21,640 --> 00:24:22,690
Have a green bean cake.

316
00:24:27,230 --> 00:24:28,970
My master loved these too.

317
00:24:32,120 --> 00:24:32,730
Yes.

318
00:24:33,600 --> 00:24:35,050
We elders

319
00:24:35,510 --> 00:24:37,050
all fancy sweet treats.

320
00:24:39,400 --> 00:24:42,050
You know my master,

321
00:24:42,360 --> 00:24:42,900
don't you?

322
00:24:46,360 --> 00:24:49,770
Since your master sent you here,

323
00:24:50,960 --> 00:24:52,420
stay here in peace.

324
00:24:53,360 --> 00:24:54,820
The academy will shield you

325
00:24:55,270 --> 00:24:58,340
as long as you stay here.

326
00:25:00,750 --> 00:25:02,860
The strange aura from the Futu Tower

327
00:25:03,120 --> 00:25:04,050
must be related to you.

328
00:25:05,310 --> 00:25:07,900
Zuo Qiu, are you too blind and foolish

329
00:25:08,120 --> 00:25:08,970
to see this?

330
00:25:09,600 --> 00:25:10,180
Mr. Zuo.

331
00:25:13,640 --> 00:25:17,290
Lifei, trust your master's arrangements.

332
00:25:17,960 --> 00:25:19,210
Some truths are better left unknown

333
00:25:19,920 --> 00:25:21,250
for your own good.

334
00:25:32,640 --> 00:25:35,010
What did Mr. Zuo say? Will he protect us?

335
00:25:35,310 --> 00:25:36,100
Smart boy.

336
00:25:36,640 --> 00:25:37,970
He wants us

337
00:25:38,120 --> 00:25:39,490
to stay inside the academy

338
00:25:39,510 --> 00:25:40,180
and never step out.

339
00:25:40,550 --> 00:25:41,530
He's right.

340
00:25:42,120 --> 00:25:43,420
If we stay here,

341
00:25:43,790 --> 00:25:44,770
Zong Quan

342
00:25:45,070 --> 00:25:46,250
won't dare act recklessly.

343
00:25:50,550 --> 00:25:52,530
The Divine Tree holds Yue's fate.

344
00:25:52,960 --> 00:25:55,100
Find out where it is at once.

345
00:25:57,550 --> 00:25:58,140
Lifei,

346
00:25:59,070 --> 00:26:01,380
when you entered the Futu Tower with Xiuyuan,

347
00:26:01,640 --> 00:26:03,490
did you spot anything resembling the Divine Tree?

348
00:26:05,990 --> 00:26:06,530
The Divine Tree?

349
00:26:07,710 --> 00:26:08,690
Why ask that suddenly?

350
00:26:09,440 --> 00:26:12,250
Xuanshanzi said the strange spirit aura in the academy

351
00:26:13,550 --> 00:26:14,290
is the Divine Tree.

352
00:26:16,550 --> 00:26:18,290
Then it has nothing to do with me.

353
00:26:19,400 --> 00:26:20,530
There's no such tree,

354
00:26:20,550 --> 00:26:21,420
nothing but books inside.

355
00:26:21,920 --> 00:26:22,820
If I'd found the Divine Tree,

356
00:26:22,840 --> 00:26:23,860
I wouldn't have feared Zong Quan.

357
00:26:24,550 --> 00:26:25,380
Makes sense.

358
00:26:28,470 --> 00:26:29,820
No matter what Zong Quan's plan is,

359
00:26:30,200 --> 00:26:30,940
our top priority

360
00:26:31,840 --> 00:26:33,900
is passing the monthly exam to stay here.

361
00:26:36,120 --> 00:26:38,180
Set aside the Divine Tree matter for now.

362
00:26:50,230 --> 00:26:51,420
This is the book from the Futu Tower.

363
00:27:02,200 --> 00:27:04,180
Let's start studying The Record of Spirit Release.

364
00:27:04,200 --> 00:27:05,100
Come on, let's go.

365
00:27:11,270 --> 00:27:13,100
This is my room.

366
00:27:13,990 --> 00:27:16,100
Don't worry, heal your wounds.

367
00:27:16,270 --> 00:27:17,340
We won't disturb you.

368
00:27:18,710 --> 00:27:19,620
- Wait. - Right.

369
00:27:20,400 --> 00:27:22,180
This is ambergris.

370
00:27:22,270 --> 00:27:23,580
Drink it with water,

371
00:27:23,790 --> 00:27:25,450
and it'll greatly aid our cultivation.

372
00:27:25,640 --> 00:27:26,660
Really?

373
00:27:27,270 --> 00:27:27,860
Let's go.

374
00:27:27,880 --> 00:27:28,900
- Go. - Get some right now.

375
00:28:09,840 --> 00:28:11,100
She's no ordinary orphan girl.

376
00:28:12,160 --> 00:28:13,180
After all these twists,

377
00:28:13,920 --> 00:28:15,450
could there truly be some fate binding us?

378
00:28:17,790 --> 00:28:19,940
