382
00:28:42,790 --> 00:28:43,730
Master.

383
00:28:43,750 --> 00:28:44,970
My heart's racing wildly.

384
00:28:45,440 --> 00:28:46,580
What's wrong with me?

385
00:28:47,160 --> 00:28:48,490
Wait for me.

386
00:28:50,200 --> 00:28:51,450
Master.

387
00:29:39,680 --> 00:29:42,050
Mr. Mo, Lifei seeks an audience.

388
00:29:49,790 --> 00:29:50,340
Come in.

389
00:30:26,120 --> 00:30:28,010
Mr. Mo, what spirit art is this?

390
00:30:28,680 --> 00:30:29,490
The Yearning Bond.

391
00:30:34,640 --> 00:30:36,420
