392
00:30:52,400 --> 00:30:53,250
What brings you here?

393
00:30:53,880 --> 00:30:55,420
I heard you excel at crafting artifacts,

394
00:30:55,440 --> 00:30:56,660
so I've come to ask

395
00:30:57,310 --> 00:30:59,050
if there is any artifact

396
00:30:59,710 --> 00:31:01,940
that can sense another's safety instantly,

397
00:31:02,120 --> 00:31:03,380
and show exactly where they are.

398
00:31:09,400 --> 00:31:10,210
For Lei Xiuyuan?

399
00:31:18,200 --> 00:31:18,970
There is such an artifact,

400
00:31:19,880 --> 00:31:22,490
but it only works if two people share

401
00:31:22,790 --> 00:31:23,580
sincere mutual affection.

402
00:31:24,440 --> 00:31:26,820
What matters is the people, not the artifact.

403
00:31:27,600 --> 00:31:28,620
Only two?

404
00:31:29,360 --> 00:31:30,420
That's far too few.

405
00:31:32,200 --> 00:31:33,010
Make it for three.

406
00:31:34,030 --> 00:31:34,690
Three?

407
00:31:37,680 --> 00:31:39,380
Besides Lei Xiuyuan, who else?

408
00:31:39,510 --> 00:31:40,420
Ji Tongzhou.

409
00:31:41,120 --> 00:31:43,340
We're like brothers, bound by unbreakable loyalty.

410
00:31:46,070 --> 00:31:47,340
The other day in the great hall,

411
00:31:47,790 --> 00:31:49,380
