412
00:31:50,160 --> 00:31:52,290
Such devotion is truly touching.

413
00:31:55,030 --> 00:31:55,490
Very well,

414
00:31:56,680 --> 00:31:57,490
I agree.

415
00:31:58,230 --> 00:32:01,420
