417
00:32:06,200 --> 00:32:09,660
Can you finish it in three days?

418
00:32:13,200 --> 00:32:14,250
Three days?

419
00:32:17,030 --> 00:32:19,100
I've read over a thousand storybooks,

420
00:32:19,680 --> 00:32:21,490
