423
00:32:25,600 --> 00:32:27,620
No matter who your beloved is,

424
00:32:28,200 --> 00:32:29,940
I'll make sure fate ties you two together.

425
00:32:40,070 --> 00:32:41,010
Fine, three days it is.

426
00:32:57,440 --> 00:32:58,340
