436
00:34:52,440 --> 00:34:52,900
This…

437
00:34:54,760 --> 00:34:56,650
Powerful spirit artifacts bear their own names.

438
00:34:58,070 --> 00:35:00,570
This place is Qianxiang room.

439
00:35:05,150 --> 00:35:05,970
Then

440
00:35:10,150 --> 00:35:12,940
